## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of sources that focus specifically on the post-Reconstruction period in the West. Additionally, while the sources provide a broad overview, they may not capture all regional variations and specific local impacts. The reliance on secondary sources also means that some interpretations may reflect the biases of the authors. Further primary research could provide a more nuanced understanding of the changes in the American West during this period.